fugitive-role-greeting = You are an Escaped Convict. Your past has finally caught up to you, but you won't let it catch you. Not today.

hunter-syndicate-role-greeting = You are a Syndicate Recovery Agent disguised as a Space Police Officer. You have been tasked with catching the fugitives hiding out in this station. Do not get caught. Do not fail.
hunter-spacepol-role-greeting = You are a Space Police Officer. You have been tasked with catching the fugitives hiding out in this station. The station's security force may not cooperate with you. Keep violence to a minimum.
hunter-russians-role-greeting = You are a Russian Space Smuggler. Spacepol has agreed to pardon your criminal record if you bring in the fugitives stowing away on this station. Avoid unneccesary killing.
hunter-bounty-role-greeting = You are a Bounty Hunter. You have been paid to execute the fugitives on board this station. Avoid unneccesary killing.

